nodes.text: Omi Vane, a Human female from Valahari and a member of the House of Vane, was the wife of Tofen Vane and was pregnant with his child around 22 BBY. Unfortunately, her husband choose to join the Clone Wars on the side of the Confederacy of Independent Systems until he realized that Count Dooku had killed his father and was eventually killed during the Battle of the Veil Nebula, leaving Omi a widow.
